parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blower motor wiring harness can cause the blower motor to stop working, leading to a loss of heating and air conditioning functionality. In some cases, the failure can also lead to a fire hazard due to the melting of wires and connectors.
symptoms: The blower motor stops working
the air conditioning or heating system fails to operate
a burning smell is present
sparks are seen
or a fire occurs.

the vehicle has a structural weakness.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall repair parts can lead to delayed or incomplete repairs, putting vehicle owners at risk of accidents or injuries due to unresolved safety issues.
